</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">μὴ ὥρασ᾽ ἵκοισθε</foreign> (Dind. for <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὥρας</foreign>) <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg007.perseus-grc1:1037\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lys.\">Lys.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1037</biblScope> </bibl>(troch.); <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὁ μὴ ὥρασι</foreign> that fellow—<tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">bad luck to him!</tr_> ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg007.perseus-grc1:391\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">391</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">μὴ ὥρασιν ἱκοίμην, εἰ</foreign>. . <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0062.tlg045:5\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Luc.\">Luc.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Salt.\">Salt.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5</biblScope> </bibl>; also <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">μὴ σύ γ᾽ εἰς ὥρας ἵκοιο</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0614.tlg001:53:7\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Babr.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">53.7</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> (cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὥρα</foreign> (C) <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0199.tlg001:1:4\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ B.\">B.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.4</biblScope> </bibl>).—For the form, cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">θύρασι, Ὀλυμπίασι.</foreign> </sense> </entryFree>"}]}